name: TheWarehouse
description:
More psycho than horror, this is my 3rd game, im actually kinda proud of this.

movement: wasd to move, e to interact, f to turn on flashlights.

play time is ~30mins.

Version 1.5 is he current, still didnt bake any light because it takes a lot of time and you only know how the end result looks after it finished.

if you find any bug or misspelles just comment and i will fix them.

Thank you.

Also qualaty is pre set to low.
